Courtesy #DStv403 TSHWANE - Traffic in Pretoria was a nightmare for many drivers on Saturday night. That's after a multiple-vehicle collision on the  N1 North left many injured. READ | Multiple vehicles involved in pile-up on N1 North in Pretoria Ten cars, a bus, a truck and a taxi were involved. Tshwane Emergency Medical Services spokesperson, Charles  Mabaso says two people have been hospitalised following the collision.